Class WCSParamsPanel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class WCSParamsPanel
extends WizardPanel
    This class implements the map option panel. It includes a set of Listeners that implement some control rules which refresh the component values that depends on those selected in the other components to avoid to choose an invalid set of options. It also includes a method (isCorrectlyConfigured()) that checks if the current set of values is enough to correctly launch a GetMap request. The information is obtained from a WCSWizardDataSource object.
